        <updateDate>2021-10-08T09:19:35Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Budget, No Pay Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits Members of Congress from being paid in a fiscal year until both chambers approve the budget resolution and pass all regular appropriations bills for that fiscal year. Retroactive pay is prohibited for such a period.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
