      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to provide that Members of Congress may not receive pay after October 1 of any fiscal year in which Congress has not approved a concurrent resolution on the budget and passed the regular appropriations bills.</title>
      </item>
